[SN]TITLE[SN]
Motorcyclist dies after A4063 Croeserw crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A motorcyclist has died following a crash with a car in Neath Port Talbot.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police said the incident, at about 08:05 GMT in Croeserw on Tuesday, involved the bike and a black Vauxhall Corsa.
The A4063 Maesteg Road was shut for about four hours after the crash.
Police have asked for anyone with information to contact them.
